title: CSO Ireland, Number of family units with children by family cycle by town, Ireland, 2006
name: CSO Ireland, Number of family units with children by family cycle by town, Ireland, 2006
description: This dataset has data on Number of family units with children by family cycle (couples or lone parents with children by family cycle) throughout towns in Ireland that have a population of over 1000. The data includes numbers and percentages for the following age range of children in family units: Pre-School, Early School, Pre-Adolescent, Adolescent, and Adult Children. The towns have been geolocated by their lat/lon position. For more info about the data go to cso.ie/census.
